sentence: Tuesday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 4,268.76.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 2.37 billion.
Declining stocks led advancers by 1.87 to 1 ratio.
There were 991 advancers and 1856 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 3 stocks reached a 52 week high and 193 reaching lows.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed down -.32% for the day; a total of -12.87 points.
Viacom Inc. ( VIAB ) had the largest percent change down (-21.48%) while Electronic Arts Inc. ( EA ) had the largest percent change gain rising 3.43%.
The Dow Jones index closed down -.08% for the day; a total of -12.67 points.

The current value is 16,014.38. International Business Machines Corporation ( IBM ) had the largest percent change down (-2.29%) while Home Depot, Inc. (The) ( HD ) had the largest percent change gain rising 1.8%.
